Lots of people have helped the sandy-haxe port, by contributing tutorials, bug
reports, patches and good old blog posts. The main contributors for the haXe releases 
were:

Thomas Pfeiffer | sandy author
Niel Drummond | initial haXe port, maintenance and neash integration
Russell Weir | sandy-hx trunk code and features implementor
Maksym Zubkov | bug fixes and tutorials
Bertil Gralvik | documentation, tutorials and website maintenance
Max Pellizzaro | tutorials
Justin Lawerance Mills and Guy Wheeler | bug reports and tutorials

If you feel you should be mentioned please contact us on the sandy mailing list.
